# 🚀 Migration Plan: Jenkins → GitHub Actions (Self-Hosted Runner Model)

## 🎯 Objective

Migrate the existing Jenkins-based CI/CD pipeline to GitHub Actions while:

* Preserving **100% of current functionality**
* Avoiding Jenkins pipeline issues (`sh`, Groovy sandbox, approvals)
* Eliminating hardcoded values
* Using secure GitHub Secrets
* Running the **same production-grade script**

---

# 🧠 Architecture Overview

## 🔴 Current (Jenkins Pipeline)

Jenkinsfile → Groovy → sh → Script → Deployment

## 🟢 Target (Hybrid Model)

GitHub Actions → Self-Hosted Runner (Jenkins VM) → Bash Script → Deployment

👉 Jenkins is **no longer used for orchestration**
👉 Jenkins VM is reused as a **runner machine**

---

