## 1️⃣ Install GitHub Runner on Jenkins VM

### Go to:

GitHub Repo → Settings → Actions → Runners → New self-hosted runner

### Run commands on Jenkins VM:

```bash
mkdir -p /u01/actions-runner
cd /u01/actions-runner

curl -o actions-runner.tar.gz -L https://github.com/actions/runner/releases/latest/download/actions-runner-linux-x64.tar.gz
tar xzf actions-runner.tar.gz
```

