# 🧩 9️⃣ Script Modifications (java_deployment.sh)

## ✅ Add at TOP (MANDATORY)

```bash
set -e
trap 'echo "❌ Script failed at line $LINENO."' ERR

# Validate required variables
required_vars=(
  JOB_NAME BRANCH BUILD_ENV REQUIRED
  REPO_WORKSPACE TOMCAT_BRANCH BUILD_USER
  GCHAT_URL DEV_GCHAT_URL
)

for var in "${required_vars[@]}"; do
  if [[ -z "${!var}" ]]; then
    echo "❌ Missing variable: $var"
    exit 1
  fi
done

# Workspace fix
WORKSPACE="${GITHUB_WORKSPACE:-$REPO_WORKSPACE/workspace}"
```

