# 🚨 Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue                   | Fix                     |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------- |
| Runner not picking job  | Check service status    |
| Script permission error | `chmod +x`              |
| Path issues             | Use `$GITHUB_WORKSPACE` |
| SSH failure             | Fix key-based auth      |
| Missing tools           | Install on VM           |

